'''迈克尔·霍顿'''（{{lang-en|'''Michael Houghton'''}}，{{bd|1949年}}），[[英国|英国]]科学家，和[[诺贝尔奖|诺贝尔奖]]获得者。1989年，他与{{tsl|en|Qui-Lim Choo|朱桂霖}}，[[郭勁宏|郭勁宏]]和[[丹尼尔·布拉德利|丹尼尔·布拉德利]](Daniel W. Bradley)共同发现了[[丙型肝炎|丙型肝炎]]<ref name="choo">{{cite journal |vauthors=Choo QL, Kuo G, Weiner AJ, Overby LR, Bradley DW, Houghton M |title=Isolation of a cDNA clone derived from a blood-borne non-A, non-B viral hepatitis genome |journal=Science |volume=244 |issue=4902 |pages=359–62 |date=April 1989 |pmid=2523562 |doi=10.1126/science.2523562|bibcode=1989Sci...244..359C |citeseerx=10.1.1.469.3592 }}</ref>。他还于1986年共同发现了[[丁型肝炎|丁型肝炎]]的[[基因组|基因组]]<ref>{{cite journal|last=Wang|first=KS |author2=[[Qui-Lim_Choo|Choo, QL]] |author3=Weiner, AJ |author4=Ou, JH |author5=Najarian, RC |author6=Thayer, RM |author7=Mullenbach, GT |author8=Denniston, KJ |author9=Gerin, JL |author10=Houghton, M|title=Structure, sequence and expression of the hepatitis delta (delta) viral genome|journal=Nature|date=9 October 1986|volume=323|issue=6088|pages=508–14|pmid=3762705|doi=10.1038/323508a0|bibcode=1986Natur.323..508W |s2cid=4265339 }}</ref>。[[丙型肝炎病毒|丙型肝炎病毒(HCV)]]的发现导致用于检测血液供应中[[丙型肝炎病毒|丙型肝炎病毒(HCV)]]的诊断试剂的迅速发展，这使通过输血获得[[丙型肝炎病毒|丙型肝炎病毒(HCV)]]的风险从三分之一减少到了约200万之一<ref>{{cite web|title=Opinion: Nobel-worthy discovery right in our backyard|url=http://www.chrcrm.org/en/node/6048|website=Canadian for Health Research|accessdate=4 September 2016|archive-date=2016-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160914165652/http://www.chrcrm.org/en/node/6048|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Science world abuzz as virologist turns down Gairdner award|url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/technology/science/science-world-abuzz-as-virologist-turns-down-gairdner-award/article10052360/|website=[[The_Globe_and_Mail|The Globe and Mail]]|accessdate=10 September 2016|archive-date=2020-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804021034/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/technology/science/science-world-abuzz-as-virologist-turns-down-gairdner-award/article10052360/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。 据估计，仅在美国，抗体测试每年就至少预防了40,000例新的感染，而在全世界范围内，预防了更多的这种情况<ref name="pioneersofmed">{{cite book|last1=Thompson|first1=Gilbert|title=Pioneers of Medicine Without a Nobel Prize|date=2014|page=209|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=_dK3CgAAQBAJ&q=%22Pioneers+of+Medicine+Without+a+Nobel+Prize%22+%22houghton%22&pg=PA206|isbn=978-1-78326-386-8|access-date=2020-11-21|archive-date=2021-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210701101227/https://books.google.com/books?id=_dK3CgAAQBAJ&q=%22Pioneers+of+Medicine+Without+a+Nobel+Prize%22+%22houghton%22&pg=PA206|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 早年生平和教育　==
1949年出生于英国，他的父亲是卡车司机和工会官员<ref name="pioneersofmed"/>。霍顿在读到有关[[路易斯·巴斯德|路易斯·巴斯德]]（Louis Pasteur）的知识后，便被启发成为一名[[微生物学|微生物学家]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Michael Houghton, PhD|url=http://www.chrcrm.org/en/rotm/michael-houghton-phd|website=Canadians for Health Research|accessdate=8 October 2016|archive-date=2012-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120614035422/http://www.chrcrm.org/en/rotm/michael-houghton-phd|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Eureka moments in research|url=http://www.aihealthsolutions.ca/news-and-events/media-centre/eureka-moments-in-research/|website=Alberta Innovates: Health Solutions|accessdate=8 October 2016|archive-date=2014-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141026061232/http://www.aihealthsolutions.ca/news-and-events/media-centre/eureka-moments-in-research/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。霍顿1972年获[[东英吉利大学|东英吉利大学]]学士学位，并于1977年获[[伦敦大学国王学院|伦敦大学国王学院]]生物学博士学位<ref name="pioneersofmed"/><ref name="ref904913078">{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=n5P696E7T0wC&q=dr+Michael+Houghton&pg=PA344|title=Liver Cirrhosis and Its Development – Google Books|accessdate=12 January 2014|isbn=978-0-7923-8760-2|last1=Boyer|first1=J.L|last2=Blum|first2=H.E|last3=Maier|first3=K.P|last4=Sauerbruch|first4=T.|last5=Stalder|first5=G.A|date=31 March 2001|archive-date=2021-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210701101243/https://books.google.com/books?id=n5P696E7T0wC&q=dr+Michael+Houghton&pg=PA344|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 科学生涯 ==
[[File:15_Hegasy_Nobel_Prize_2020_HepC.jpg|thumb]]

然后，他在白金汉郡塞尔研究实验室工作，在1982年成为{{le|希龙公司|Chiron Corporation}}的非甲非乙型肝炎部主管。<ref>Biographie in Boyer u. a. (Hrsg.): ''Liver Cirrhosis and Its Development,'' Kluwer 2001.</ref>正是在{{le|希龙公司|Chiron Corporation}}，霍顿与来自[[美国疾病控制与预防中心|美国疾病控制与预防中心]]的同事{{tsl|en|Qui-Lim Choo|朱桂霖}}，[[郭勁宏|郭勁宏]]和[[丹尼尔·布拉德利|丹尼尔·布拉德利]]一起首次发现了[[丙型肝炎病毒|丙型肝炎病毒(HCV)]]的证据<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Houghton|first1=M|title=The long and winding road leading to the identification of the hepatitis C virus.|journal=J. Hepatol.|date=2009|volume=51|issue=5|pages=939–948|doi=10.1016/j.jhep.2009.08.004|pmid=19781804|doi-access=free}}</ref>。

在20世纪80年代初CDC的[[丹尼尔·布拉德利|丹尼尔·布拉德利]]从[[黑猩猩|黑猩猩]]的血清中分离了后来称为[[丙肝病毒|丙肝病毒]]的非甲非乙型肝炎病毒。霍顿得以与布拉德利协作克隆这些病毒，并开发了一种测验血液的方法，在20世纪90年代初用于[[肝硬化|肝硬化]]和[[肝癌|肝癌]]患者。

2013年，阿尔伯塔大学霍顿的团队证明，源自单一丙型肝炎病毒株的疫苗可有效对抗这种病毒的所有病毒株<ref>{{cite journal|last=Law|first=JL |author2=Chen, C |author3=Wong, J |author4=Hockman, D |author5=Santer, DM |author6=Frey, SE |author7=Belshe, RB |author8=Wakita, T |author9=Bukh, J |author10=Jones, CT |author11=Rice, CM |author12=Abrignani, S |author13=Tyrrell, DL |author14=Houghton, M.|title=A hepatitis C virus (HCV) vaccine comprising envelope glycoproteins gpE1/gpE2 derived from a single isolate elicits broad cross-genotype neutralizing antibodies in humans.|journal=PLOS ONE|date=19 March 2013|volume=8|issue=3|pmid=23527266|doi=10.1371/journal.pone.0059776 |pmc=3602185 |pages=e59776|bibcode=2013PLoSO...859776L }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Houghton|first1=M|last2=Law|first2=J|last3=Tyrrell|first3=DL|title=An inactivated hepatitis C virus vaccine on the horizon?|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_gastroenterology_2013-08_145_2/page/285|journal=Gastroenterology|date=2013|volume=145|issue=2|pages=285–288|doi=10.1053/j.gastro.2013.06.029|pmid=23806539}}</ref>。截至2020年，该疫苗正在进行非临床试验<ref>{{Cite web|title=University of Alberta virologist awarded Nobel Prize in Physiology or Medicine|url=https://www.eurekalert.org/pub_releases/2020-10/uoaf-uoa100520.php|access-date=6 October 2020|website=EurekAlert!|language=en|archive-date=2021-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210701101249/https://www.eurekalert.org/pub_releases/2020-10/uoaf-uoa100520.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 奖项 ==
*1992年，他与他的团队成员同获{{le|美国血库协会|AABB}}[[卡尔·兰德斯泰纳纪念奖|卡尔·兰德斯泰纳纪念奖]]。
*1993年，他与布拉德利获得了[[羅伯·柯霍獎|羅伯·柯霍獎]]。
*1994年，获{{le|美国胃肠病协会|American Gastroenterological Association}}{{le|威廉·博蒙特奖|William Beaumont Prize}}。
*2000年，获[[拉斯克奖|拉斯克奖]] 
*2013年，获加拿大[[盖尔德纳国际奖|盖尔德纳国际奖]]，但霍顿拒绝领奖，因为两位同事[[郭勁宏|郭勁宏]]（台灣人）、{{tsl|en|Qui-Lim Choo|朱桂霖}}（新加坡人）没能一起获奖。<ref>[http://www.cbc.ca/news/health/story/2013/03/20/gairdner-awards.html Canadian declines prestigious Gairdner award for medical research.] {{Wayback|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/health/story/2013/03/20/gairdner-awards.html |date=20130514061322 }} [[CBC/Radio-Canada|CBC/Radio-Canada]] (cbc.ca); abgerufen am 20. März 2013</ref>
*2020年，荣獲[[諾貝爾生理學或醫學獎|諾貝爾生理學或醫學獎]]。<ref>{{cite web |title=The Nobel Prize in Physiology or Medicine 2020 |url=https://www.nobelprize.org/prizes/medicine/2020/summary/ |website=NobelPrize.org |language=en |access-date=2020-10-05 |archive-date=2020-10-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201005113756/https://www.nobelprize.org/prizes/medicine/2020/summary// |dead-url=no }}</ref>

